@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### 회원가입
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "apiuser{{$timestamp}}",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 로그인
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "javakim",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 로그인 실패
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "javakim",
  "password": "wrong-password"
}

### 토큰 재발급
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzM4NCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJqYXZha2ltIiwidHlwZSI6InJlZnJlc2giLCJpYXQiOjE3NzM2NzI0NTksImV4cCI6MTc3NDI3NzI1OX0.iVaE9f6PbVKU1gknQS9ZlAMrcaEp3QL7Gp3QIsoF8r438ysFwlg_OlPSetQqOW18"
}

### 토큰 재발급 실패
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "invalid-token"
}

